Замена: \(2^x=t\)
$$t-\frac{240}{t-1}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2-t-240}{t-1}\geq 0\\ \frac{(t-16)(t+15)}{t-1}\geq 0$$
$$\displaystyle \left[
\begin{gathered}
\begin{cases}
t \geq - 15 \hfill \\
t < 1 \hfill \\
\end{cases}\\
t \geq 16 \hfill
\end{gathered} \right.$$

Вернемся к замене:
$$
\left[
\begin{gathered}
\begin{cases}
2^{x} \geq -15\\
2^{x} < 2^{0}
\end{cases}\\
2^{x} \geq 2^{4}
\end{gathered}
\right.$$
Т. к. \(2^x>0\), то:
$$
\left[
\begin{gathered}
x< 0 \hfill \\
x\geq 4 \hfill
\end{gathered}
\right.$$
Ответ: \(x\in (-\infty;0)\cup [4;+\infty)\).
